1
00:00:13,480 --> 00:00:14,810
Once I become the mayor,

2
00:00:15,640 --> 00:00:16,970
this director position

3
00:00:17,320 --> 00:00:18,120
will be yours.

4
00:00:20,160 --> 00:00:22,290
Thank you for your support, Director.

5
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:23,800
I heard Wang Shiqi

6
00:00:23,880 --> 00:00:27,080
is going to the graveyard tonight to exorcise the spirit.

7
00:00:27,720 --> 00:00:28,650
An infant spirit

8
00:00:28,880 --> 00:00:30,480
isn't that easy to exorcise.

9
00:00:30,560 --> 00:00:32,490
Even if he gets lucky and succeeds,

10
00:00:32,920 --> 00:00:34,160
the whole town knows

11
00:00:34,480 --> 00:00:35,840
that my son is possessed.

12
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:36,960
How will he explain it?

13
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:38,620
He'll still get fired anyway.

14
00:00:39,640 --> 00:00:40,240
Director,

15
00:00:40,320 --> 00:00:41,960
you are truly a master strategist.

16
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:43,320
Such a brilliant plan.

17
00:00:47,160 --> 00:00:47,490
Come.

18
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:48,960
Come.

19
00:00:56,360 --> 00:00:58,420
The Yin energy here is the strongest.

20
00:00:59,080 --> 00:01:01,280
We will perform the ritual at midnight.

21
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:02,400
Perhaps

22
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:05,459
we can lure the infant spirit out.

23
00:01:05,880 --> 00:01:07,010
Then with the help of

24
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:09,240
this Yin Fetus Umbilical Severing Array,

25
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:10,240
we can force it away.

26
00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:11,039
Brother Wang,

27
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:13,200
save me!

28
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:16,160
You stinky executioner!

29
00:01:16,160 --> 00:01:16,760
Hero Wang.

30
00:01:17,039 --> 00:01:17,500
Save me!

31
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:19,200
I'll leave this place to you.

32
00:02:50,200 --> 00:02:52,079
They are multiples.

33
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:54,560
No wonder she's showing so much.

34
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:55,640
Here I go.

35
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,820
Little ghosts.

36
00:03:10,880 --> 00:03:13,340
I warn you in the name of the Yin Executioner.

37
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,300
Even though

38
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,920
I really do want a son.

39
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:20,120
But

40
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:21,240
personally,

41
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,200
I still want to

42
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,720
experience the process.

43
00:03:25,560 --> 00:03:27,020
Why am I telling them this?

44
00:03:27,200 --> 00:03:28,930
They don't understand anyway.

45
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,320
Listen up.

46
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,640
Your path here defies the righteous way.

47
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:33,760
It violates heavenly laws.

48
00:03:33,760 --> 00:03:35,960
Even if born, you won't take human form.

49
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,640
Today, I sever the umbilical cord

50
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:39,040
and send your souls back.

51
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,660
If you refuse to leave,

52
00:03:41,040 --> 00:03:43,440
you'll become sacrifices for my sword.

53
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,579
Little ghosts.

54
00:03:58,040 --> 00:03:59,760
Do you want to be my son that badly?

55
00:03:59,760 --> 00:04:00,200
But

56
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:01,440
this kind of thing

57
00:04:01,480 --> 00:04:03,040
depends on fate.

58
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,120
Why so fierce?

59
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,580
What are you doing?

60
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,130
Careful, or I'll spank you.

61
00:04:11,160 --> 00:04:12,090
What do you want?

62
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,240
Where did he go?

63
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:22,760
I think

64
00:04:23,640 --> 00:04:24,560
he went to find his

65
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:26,090
parents from his past life.

66
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:28,720
Come.

67
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:32,960
In the future, this director position

68
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:33,760
will be yours.

69
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,120
Thank you, Director.

70
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:36,880
Bottoms up.

71
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,080
Come, son.

72
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:44,720
Honey.

73
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,330
The Director

74
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:47,480
and his son want you

75
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,760
to go over for a drink.

76
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,200
Honey.

77
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:54,800
This bitch

78
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,440
fell asleep so early.

79
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:59,020
Could it be that she

80
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:00,160
and that Wang boy

81
00:05:00,800 --> 00:05:02,530
actually did it these few days?

82
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,480
Let's go, honey.

83
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:13,160
Honey!

84
00:05:14,000 --> 00:05:14,760
It's been so long.

85
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,120
What are these two doing?

86
00:05:16,120 --> 00:05:17,120
Let me take a look.

87
00:05:26,040 --> 00:05:26,880
Good girl.

88
00:05:27,320 --> 00:05:28,600
Go to sleep.

89
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:40,220
Wang Shiqi!

90
00:05:40,520 --> 00:05:41,320
You jinx!

91
00:05:41,480 --> 00:05:42,880
Get out of Taohua Town immediately!

92
00:05:42,880 --> 00:05:43,240
Get out!

93
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:45,640
Get out! Get out!

94
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,760
Everyone, calm down.

95
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,490
Listen to me.

96
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:48,960
Wang Shiqi is not that kind of person.

97
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:49,760
It's no use saying anything.

98
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:50,600
Kick them all out.

99
00:05:50,600 --> 00:05:51,400
Wait a minute.

100
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:53,460
I can prove it to everyone.

101
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,360
Prove what?

102
00:05:58,520 --> 00:05:59,320
Why is it gone?

103
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:00,320
Why is the belly gone?

104
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,250
What's going on?

105
00:06:01,280 --> 00:06:02,210
Everyone, look.

106
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,080
Are these two women

107
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,960
in front of us safe and sound now?

108
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,480
What on earth is going on?

109
00:06:07,480 --> 00:06:08,560
The so-called infant spirit...

110
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,240
Everyone.

111
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,960
The infant spirit has been driven back to where it belongs.

112
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:16,020
As the saying goes,

113
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:18,160
every wrong has its cause, every debt its debtor.

114
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:20,240
And the person causing trouble behind the scenes

115
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:22,160
will eventually get their retribution.

116
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:24,440
When the time comes, everyone will naturally know the truth.

117
00:06:24,440 --> 00:06:25,360
So what?

118
00:06:25,840 --> 00:06:26,370
Who knows

119
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,560
if this is some evil trick you are playing?

120
00:06:28,560 --> 00:06:29,160
That's right.

121
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:29,560
Yeah.

122
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,080
Yes.

123
00:06:30,080 --> 00:06:30,880
Get out. Get out.

124
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:33,280
Get out. Get out. Get out.

125
00:06:33,280 --> 00:06:34,810
You are jumping up and down,

126
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:37,080
trying to kick me out.

127
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,360
Someone is behind this, right?

128
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:40,880
No one ordered us.

129
00:06:41,080 --> 00:06:41,760
Get out.

130
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:44,200
Get out. Get out.

131
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:44,760
Shut up.

132
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:45,280
Get out.

133
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,360
What are you shouting about?

134
00:06:46,360 --> 00:06:46,880
Director Song.

135
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:47,760
Didn't you ask us to...

136
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:48,220
Shut up.

137
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,020
Wang Shiqi.

138
00:06:53,360 --> 00:06:53,960
Hero Wang.

139
00:06:54,080 --> 00:06:54,940
Immortal Wang.

140
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:56,720
Please save my son.

141
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,200
Save the Song family.

142
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:00,060
If you are willing to help,

143
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,560
you will be the great benefactor of the Song family,

144
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:03,160
and our second parent.

145
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:05,960
You are too polite, Director Song.

146
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:07,890
I wouldn't dare have a son like you.

147
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:08,690
Mr. Wang,

148
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,200
I beg you.

149
00:07:10,880 --> 00:07:11,480
All right.

150
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:12,920
Since

151
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,620
Director Song has said so,

152
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,340
then in front of everyone,

153
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:17,960
confess all the bad things

154
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:20,160
you and your son have done over the years

155
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:22,560
in full detail.

156
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,040
Mr. Wang,

157
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:29,040
this concerns the reputation of my Song family.

158
00:07:29,040 --> 00:07:29,560
Can we...

159
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,420
Too difficult?

160
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,640
If that's the case,

161
00:07:32,640 --> 00:07:33,280
forget it.

162
00:07:33,960 --> 00:07:34,760
Wait a minute.

163
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,200
I'll talk.

164
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,440
I'll talk.

165
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:46,500
This is all a farce directed and acted out

166
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,960
by me and my son.

167
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:50,290
It was to frame Hero Wang

168
00:07:51,080 --> 00:07:51,600
and

169
00:07:51,840 --> 00:07:53,370
ruin Mayor Su's reputation

170
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,600
to drag him down from the mayor's position.

171
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,200
Song Ping,

172
00:07:56,360 --> 00:07:58,440
you two are truly despicable and shameful.

173
00:07:58,440 --> 00:07:58,880
Yes.

174
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,880
I was obsessed.

175
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:04,280
Hero Wang,

176
00:08:05,080 --> 00:08:06,360
I beg you to save my son.

177
00:08:08,360 --> 00:08:09,560
Why are you all just standing there?

178
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:10,760
Help me beg Hero Wang.

179
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:12,720
Mr. Wang,

180
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:13,520
please.

181
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,360
Mr. Wang,

182
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:15,320
I beg you.

183
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:16,680
Please.

184
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,020
This is too shameless.

185
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,280
Please, Mr. Wang.

186
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:25,690
Mr. Wang,

187
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,800
what exactly happened to my son?

188
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:31,040
Summoning infant spirits is inherently immoral.

189
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,970
It's natural to suffer a backlash.

190
00:08:33,480 --> 00:08:35,280
You brought this upon yourself.

191
00:08:35,679 --> 00:08:36,280
Mr. Wang,

192
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,299
please be generous

193
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:39,340
and save my son.

194
00:08:39,559 --> 00:08:42,289
I will never make things difficult for you again.

195
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:44,840
When I repelled the infant spirit,

196
00:08:44,840 --> 00:08:46,040
under normal circumstances,

197
00:08:46,040 --> 00:08:48,100
it should have returned to its mother

198
00:08:48,160 --> 00:08:49,690
and waited to be born again.

199
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,560
But this time,

200
00:08:50,640 --> 00:08:51,570
it's different.

201
00:08:52,160 --> 00:08:53,480
It's haunting Master Song.

202
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,480
This can only mean

203
00:08:54,560 --> 00:08:56,840
that the infant spirit's mother is no longer in this world,

204
00:08:56,840 --> 00:08:58,360
and that there's a deep connection

205
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:00,360
between the spirit and Master Song.

206
00:09:00,680 --> 00:09:01,440
Spit it out.

207
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:04,010
What terrible things have you done

208
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:05,160
to cause the infant spirit to die young

209
00:09:05,160 --> 00:09:06,220
and fail to grow up?

210
00:09:07,560 --> 00:09:08,080
My son

211
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:09,780
may be a bit of a womanizer,

212
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:10,760
but he wouldn't go so far as

213
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,880
to be this crazy.

214
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,480
I don't care about these habits.

215
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:14,240
I'm telling you,

216
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,240
if you don't tell the truth,

217
00:09:15,240 --> 00:09:16,900
I can't find a solution at all.

218
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:19,720
Your son is now haunted by an infant spirit.

219
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:21,620
He will slowly shrink into a fetus

220
00:09:21,680 --> 00:09:23,940
and eventually turn into a pool of blood.

221
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,040
See that?

222
00:09:25,760 --> 00:09:27,040
If you want to save him,

223
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:28,840
tell the truth.

224
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:29,960
Otherwise, you will eventually

225
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:32,080
see your son grow younger

226
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:33,920
and return to the womb.

227
00:09:43,040 --> 00:09:43,680
Ruyan.

228
00:09:45,160 --> 00:09:45,960
Who is Ruyan?

229
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,160
Ruyan

230
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:50,980
is the top courtesan of Yihong Pavilion.

231
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:53,040
The first time my son saw her,

232
00:09:53,160 --> 00:09:54,890
he was completely mesmerized.

233
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:56,600
From then on, the two were inseparable.

234
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:57,880
She actually thought about

235
00:09:57,880 --> 00:09:59,610
marrying into the Song family.

236
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,580
Director Song.

237
00:10:02,200 --> 00:10:04,330
I'm carrying the Song family's child.

238
00:10:04,680 --> 00:10:06,960
You think you can get rid of me with this little money?

239
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:09,280
I am going to be the young mistress of the Song family.
